reviewText: Nicely done! Shows you many variations of the tricks and proper bike set-up! Great video!!

This DVD is good enough if you don't mind its price. You can gain much more by reading published articles on Wheelies on WikiHow and by a guy named Osvath. You can Google these. As far as video goes, there are videos all over the YouTube on wheelies. I have seen better stunters at circuses. Woods comes across a bit conceited.
